e":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75c929863ee913a844181b36753ae2c65e5a7114","tid":744952,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:16:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d665a6c70c87c96e51162c992ec158fb6ae2021c","tid":744952,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"CE AL體制有佢既優點<br />\nCE升中六時殺左一批<br />\n得7-8分個d最輕鬆,疊埋心水出去做野或直接報差佬<br />\n<br />\n10-13 分個d,都可以有重讀中五機會<br />\n14+分兩批，原校升讀/出去搵學校<br />\n當中英文冇d，就點都要考多次<br />\n一黎博高d grade, 二黎keep住操英文程度AL唔會太差<br />\n<br />\n升中六後，CE成積最好個d會自然報晒A math，AL無論理科or文科，全部都係cls lvl，為左增加入大學機會，好多人都報3AL，心理未成熟既話根本係冇能力面對咁既課程，所以中六時每個人都會好珍惜讀AL機會,全部自動自覺，每個人都博到盡，唔會有任何僥倖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個CE AL體制其實好變態，壓力係逐步遞增，但係個制度其實好合理，每個人考完後都會知道自己下一步要點做。<br />\n<br />\n你問AL年代既人，成世人最認真讀書絕對係AL個兩年，迫你認真為自己前途打算，令人更成熟，更懂得珍惜，經歷完AL後，大學課程反而easy job，論壓力，FYP其實連CE都不如。一個經AL jupas 獲得既大學學位，含金量絕對高過以後用錢買返來d所謂master。所以有d人好多年後再搵工，依然會好自豪咁寫埋AL成積，呢個係佢地人生既重要履歷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到左dse 年代，不知不覺學歷貶值，唔好話學位已經不是甚麼，連master都係通街一地都係，dse 12345個分，真係唔知有幾多老細 care(分分鐘睇都未識睇)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a9431d43cbea3283d214f44b7d5fd464c5a6a0","tid":744952,"uid":194474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"303a714f714999acbada3286890fab331d8eb62e","tid":744952,"uid":183146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95620cba77249b48b8f814b89f43d45b621aadd2","tid":744952,"uid":194474,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"DSE雞<br />\n但支持AL撚<br />\n想考都冇得考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"Ching 你最尾咪考左GCE 囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T01:54:01.000Z","msg":"AL最正係課程又深又廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGCE課程係廣而不深<br />\nDSE係深而不廣（相比於GCE)<br />\n我兩樣都考哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母 點解唔可以考AL一次滿足我2個願望？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042ba7fbb3781f33b8d87458f50acdb640e9bf46","tid":744952,"uid":183146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7a9431d43cbea3283d214f44b7d5fd464c5a6a0","tid":744952,"uid":194474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"303a714f714999acbada3286890fab331d8eb62e","tid":744952,"uid":183146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95620cba77249b48b8f814b89f43d45b621aadd2","tid":744952,"uid":194474,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"DSE雞<br />\n但支持AL撚<br />\n想考都冇得考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"Ching 你最尾咪考左GCE 囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T01:54:01.000Z","msg":"AL最正係課程又深又廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGCE課程係廣而不深<br />\nDSE係深而不廣（相比於GCE)<br />\n我兩樣都考哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母 點解唔可以考AL一次滿足我2個願望？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T02:58:31.000Z","msg":"咁你都唔好屌我老母ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80d25627cd1b27179115605fc700a726d1d33a4","tid":744952,"uid":194474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"042ba7fbb3781f33b8d87458f50acdb640e9bf46","tid":744952,"uid":183146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7a9431d43cbea3283d214f44b7d5fd464c5a6a0","tid":744952,"uid":194474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"303a714f714999acbada3286890fab331d8eb62e","tid":744952,"uid":183146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"Ching 你最尾咪考左GCE 囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T01:54:01.000Z","msg":